{"tid":438451,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一日一句","createTime":"2017-10-17T02:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T08:56:16.000Z","uid":32063,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf599491f4812bd1c6386fc16359f4193710d36","tid":438451,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T02:38:31.000Z","msg":"20171017<br />\n<br />\n依個世界就係有人鍾意浪費時間，但明明浪費時間就係等於浪費生命。"},{"pid":"0a17dfa3b972017d09db8ffe7a624f4f81e28ca1","tid":438451,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:07:35.000Z","msg":"201711018<br />\n不去習慣，不去妥協"},{"pid":"ed31c97b4b73029d3e3e93d4de99ab72741ff041","tid":438451,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"20171019<br />\n人應該在乎活著既時候，而唔係只在乎死後虛無縹緲既幻想"},{"pid":"742a5168516ed78c9decf32d5f273363f5c63cf1","tid":438451,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T05:06:16.000Z","msg":"20171020<br />\n人生三大偽命題 入大學 結婚 生仔"},{"pid":"e0f6269511321ffc9c8fcf5457e446282a851c0a","tid":438451,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:14:33.000Z","msg":"20171023<br />\n對老人黎講經濟唔好係一時姐，對年經黎講係一直既事"},{"pid":"9a791b11e85d9aba6eeb3de378a9201161187306","tid":438451,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:29:57.000Z","msg":"死亡離大家太遙遠，遙遠到學懂夢想同珍惜都唔係一件容易既事。"},{"pid":"85b687f287f53f4286ea622b40ce72cc856ce01c","tid":438451,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T07:53:18.000Z","msg":"20171025<br />\n<br />\n公司最令人安心既地方可能得廁所。"},{"pid":"457fb5be628ed31ae1e469e704de2dfb7eb93e27","tid":438451,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"20171026<br />\n被需要的感覺，係人生存既意義"},{"pid":"edfaf4ce6a26e96c31aa1834e7514efba49e01bb","tid":438451,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T07:38:05.000Z","msg":"20171027<br />\n